### Notification Service API Test Examples
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api/notifications
@authToken = your-jwt-token-here

### ============================================================================
### Device Token Management
### ============================================================================

### Register iOS Device Token
POST {{baseUrl}}/tokens
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "device_id": "ios-device-12345",
  "fcm_token": "fcm-token-example-ios-abcdef123456",
  "platform": "ios",
  "app_version": "1.0.0"
}

### Register Android Device Token
POST {{baseUrl}}/tokens
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "device_id": "android-device-67890",
  "fcm_token": "fcm-token-example-android-xyz789",
  "platform": "android",
  "app_version": "1.0.0"
}

### Register Web Device Token
POST {{baseUrl}}/tokens
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "device_id": "web-browser-uuid",
  "fcm_token": "fcm-token-example-web-browser",
  "platform": "web"
}

### Deactivate Device Token
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/tokens/token-uuid-here
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### ============================================================================
### Send Notifications
### ============================================================================

### Send Visit Reminder (High Priority)
POST {{baseUrl}}/send
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "user-uuid-here",
  "type": "visit_reminder",
  "title": "Visit Reminder",
  "body": "Your visit with John Doe starts in 30 minutes",
  "data": {
    "visit_id": "visit-uuid-123",
    "client_id": "client-uuid-456",
    "client_name": "John Doe",
    "scheduled_start": "2025-10-03T10:30:00Z",
    "location": "Vessel ABC"
  },
  "priority": "high"
}

### Send Team Alert (Urgent)
POST {{baseUrl}}/send
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "user-uuid-here",
  "type": "team_alert",
  "title": "Urgent: Team Alert",
  "body": "Emergency situation on Vessel XYZ requires immediate response",
  "data": {
    "alert_type": "emergency",
    "location": "Vessel XYZ",
    "severity": "high",
    "timestamp": "2025-10-03T14:30:00Z"
  },
  "priority": "high"
}

### Send Sync Update
POST {{baseUrl}}/send
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "user-uuid-here",
  "type": "sync_update",
  "title": "Sync Complete",
  "body": "Your data has been synchronized successfully. 5 items updated.",
  "data": {
    "sync_id": "sync-uuid-789",
    "items_synced": 5,
    "sync_type": "full",
    "completed_at": "2025-10-03T15:00:00Z"
  },
  "priority": "normal"
}

### Send Family Update
POST {{baseUrl}}/send
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "family-member-uuid",
  "type": "family_update",
  "title": "Visit Completed",
  "body": "Care visit for John Doe has been completed successfully",
  "data": {
    "visit_id": "visit-uuid-123",
    "client_id": "client-uuid-456",
    "client_name": "John Doe",
    "completed_at": "2025-10-03T11:00:00Z",
    "nurse_name": "Jane Smith"
  },
  "priority": "normal"
}

### ============================================================================
### Notification History
### ============================================================================

### Get Notifications (Default Pagination)
GET {{baseUrl}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get Notifications (Custom Pagination)
GET {{baseUrl}}?limit=20&offset=0
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get Notifications (Page 2)
GET {{baseUrl}}?limit=20&offset=20
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Mark Notification as Read
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/notification-uuid-here/read
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### ============================================================================
### Notification Preferences
### ============================================================================

### Get Current Preferences
GET {{baseUrl}}/preferences
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Update Preferences - Enable All
PUT {{baseUrl}}/preferences
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "visit_reminders_enabled": true,
  "team_alerts_enabled": true,
  "sync_updates_enabled": true,
  "family_updates_enabled": true
}

### Update Preferences - Disable Visit Reminders
PUT {{baseUrl}}/preferences
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "visit_reminders_enabled": false
}

### Update Preferences - Set Quiet Hours
PUT {{baseUrl}}/preferences
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quiet_hours_start": "22:00",
  "quiet_hours_end": "08:00"
}

### Update Preferences - Disable Sync Updates with Quiet Hours
PUT {{baseUrl}}/preferences
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sync_updates_enabled": false,
  "quiet_hours_start": "23:00",
  "quiet_hours_end": "07:00"
}

### Update Preferences - Remove Quiet Hours
PUT {{baseUrl}}/preferences
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quiet_hours_start": null,
  "quiet_hours_end": null
}

### ============================================================================
### Error Cases
### ============================================================================

### Invalid Platform
POST {{baseUrl}}/tokens
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "device_id": "test-device",
  "fcm_token": "test-token",
  "platform": "invalid-platform"
}

### Missing Required Fields
POST {{baseUrl}}/tokens
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "device_id": "test-device"
}

### Invalid Notification Type
POST {{baseUrl}}/send
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "user-uuid-here",
  "type": "invalid_type",
  "title": "Test",
  "body": "Test notification"
}

### Invalid Priority
POST {{baseUrl}}/send
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "user-uuid-here",
  "type": "visit_reminder",
  "title": "Test",
  "body": "Test notification",
  "priority": "invalid-priority"
}

### Invalid Quiet Hours Format
PUT {{baseUrl}}/preferences
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quiet_hours_start": "25:00"
}

### ============================================================================
### Batch Testing Scenarios
### ============================================================================

### Scenario 1: New User Setup
# 1. Register device token
# 2. Get default preferences
# 3. Update preferences
# 4. Send test notification

### Scenario 2: Multi-Device User
# 1. Register iOS device
# 2. Register Android device
# 3. Send notification (should go to both)
# 4. Deactivate one device
# 5. Send notification (should go to remaining device)

### Scenario 3: Quiet Hours Testing
# 1. Set quiet hours (22:00 - 08:00)
# 2. Send normal priority notification during quiet hours (should be blocked)
# 3. Send high priority team alert during quiet hours (should go through)
# 4. Send notification outside quiet hours (should go through)

### Scenario 4: Preference Testing
# 1. Disable visit reminders
# 2. Send visit reminder (should be blocked)
# 3. Send team alert (should go through)
# 4. Re-enable visit reminders
# 5. Send visit reminder (should go through)
